  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/CoreWLAN\/CWSecurity\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T14:35:08Z\n---\n\n# CWSecurity\n\n**Enumeration**\n\nCoreWLAN security types.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nenum CWSecurity\n```\n\n## Constants\n\n- **CWSecurity.none**: Open System authentication.\n- **CWSecurity.WEP**: WEP security.\n- **CWSecurity.wpaPersonal**: WPA Personal authentication.\n- **CWSecurity.wpaPersonalMixed**: WPA\/WPA2 Personal authentication.\n- **CWSecurity.wpa2Personal**: WPA2 Personal authentication.\n- **CWSecurity.personal**: Personal authentication.\n- **CWSecurity.dynamicWEP**: Dynamic WEP security.\n- **CWSecurity.wpaEnterprise**: WPA Enterprise authentication.\n- **CWSecurity.wpaEnterpriseMixed**: WPA\/WPA2 Enterprise authentication.\n- **CWSecurity.wpa2Enterprise**: WPA2 Enterprise authentication.\n- **CWSecurity.enterprise**: Enterprise authentication.\n- **CWSecurity.wpa3Personal**: WPA3 Personal authentication.\n- **CWSecurity.wpa3Enterprise**: WPA3 Enterprise authentication.\n- **CWSecurity.wpa3Transition**: WPA3 Transition (WPA3\/WPA2 Personal) authentication.\n- **CWSecurity.unknown**: Unknown security type.\n\n## Enumeration Cases\n\n- **CWSecurity.OWE**\n- **CWSecurity.oweTransition**\n\n## Initializers\n\n- **init(rawValue:)**\n\n## Enumerations\n\n- **CWChannelBand**: CoreWLAN channel bands.\n- **CWChannelWidth**: CoreWLAN channel widths.\n- **CWCipherKeyFlags**: Cipher key flags.\n- **CWErr**\n- **CWEventType**: Wi-Fi event types.\n- **CWIBSSModeSecurity**: IBSS mode security types.\n- **CWInterfaceMode**: Wi-Fi interface operating modes.\n- **CWKeychainDomain**: Keychain domain types that CoreWLAN keychain methods use.\n- **CWPHYMode**: CoreWLAN physical layer modes.\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- BitwiseCopyable\n- Equatable\n- Hashable\n- RawRepresentable\n- Sendable\n- SendableMetatype\n\n",
